Here are the list of examples to be included in the class:

MPI:


1. hello_world.f, hello_world.c :
Simple examples of messaging

2. numerical_integ.c:
Domain decomposition example of doing numerical integration using the midpt rule using MPI

numerical_integ2.c:
Domain decomposition example that uses a collective communicator  - MPI_Reduce

3. matmult.f:
Functional decompostion examples of multiplying two matrices

4. array_search1.c, array_search2.c: 
Examples of using collective communicators in an MPI program where each
processor searches a section of a data array until finds a specific number and
notifies the rest to searching

5. numerical_integ_err.c: 
Examples of an MPI program with an error.




